{"title":"Hexo竟然可以展示PDF","slug":"Hexo竟然可以展示PDF","date":"2020-07-03T09:06:02.000Z","updated":"2020-07-03T09:06:02.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo竟然可以展示PDF.json","excerpt":"hexo-pdf插件一键搞定，页面展示PDF<br>","covers":["https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703172935.png","https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703173123.png"],"content":"<p>hexo-pdf插件一键搞定，页面展示PDF<br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装hexo-pdf\"><a href=\"#安装hexo-pdf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装hexo-pdf\"></a>安装hexo-pdf</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save hexo-pdf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h2><p>使用本地资源，可以在markdown文件路径下创建一个同名文件夹，其内放pdf文件<br>例如：<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703172935.png\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703173018.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>在需要的文章添加如下语句：<br><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% pdf mydocument.pdf %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>使用外部资源同理，</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% pdf https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Justlovesmile&#x2F;CDN&#x2F;pdf&#x2F;小作文讲义.pdf %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"效果\"><a href=\"#效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"效果\"></a>效果</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703173123.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n","more":"</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装hexo-pdf\"><a href=\"#安装hexo-pdf\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装hexo-pdf\"></a>安装hexo-pdf</h2><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install --save hexo-pdf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"使用\"><a href=\"#使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"使用\"></a>使用</h2><p>使用本地资源，可以在markdown文件路径下创建一个同名文件夹，其内放pdf文件<br>例如：<br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703172935.png\" alt=\"\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703173018.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>在需要的文章添加如下语句：<br><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% pdf mydocument.pdf %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><br>使用外部资源同理，</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#123;% pdf https:&#x2F;&#x2F;cdn.jsdelivr.net&#x2F;gh&#x2F;Justlovesmile&#x2F;CDN&#x2F;pdf&#x2F;小作文讲义.pdf %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"效果\"><a href=\"#效果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"效果\"></a>效果</h2><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Justlovesmile/CDN2/post/20200703173123.png\" alt=\"\"></p>","categories":[{"name":"博客相关","path":"api/categories/博客相关.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Hexo","path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"},{"name":"PDF","path":"api/tags/PDF.json"},{"name":"npm","path":"api/tags/npm.json"}]}